,"text":"# C4 — Component (L3)\n*internals of one container*","node_type":"md","color":"#475569"},{"id":"g2_title","x":5200.0,"y":170.0,"width":380.0,"height":90.0,"text":"# Component — API Application\nC4 Level 3: components inside the **API Application** container.","node_type":"md"},{"id":"g2_legend","x":5840.0,"y":170.0,"width":410.0,"height":220.0,"text":"## Legend\n- **[Component]** (palest C4 blue `#85bbf0`) — a part inside this container; states its implementation tech.\n- **[Container]** (`#438dd5`) — a sibling deployable (the SPA caller).\n- **[DB]** (cyan `#06b6d4`) — a datastore.\n- The **API Application** boundary = nodes sharing `group`.\n- Edges are directed, labeled with intent + protocol.","node_type":"md"},{"id":"g2_spa","x":5200.0,"y":380.0,"width":220.0,"height":100.0,"text":"[Container] Single-Page App\n[React]","node_type":"text","color":"#438dd5"},{"id":"g2_signin","x":5200.0,"y":540.0,"width":250.0,"height":120.0,"text":"Sign In Controller\n[Component: Spring REST Controller]\nLets users sign in.","node_type":"idea","color":"#85bbf0","group":"API Application"},{"id":"g2_accCtrl","x":5500.0,"y":540.0,"width":250.0,"height":120.0,"text":"Accounts Summary Controller\n[Component: Spring REST Controller]","node_type":"idea","color":"#85bbf0","group":"API Application"},{"id":"g2_security","x":5200.0,"y":700.0,"width":250.0,"height":120.0,"text":"Security Component\n[Component: Spring Bean]\nValidates credentials.","node_type":"idea","color":"#85bbf0","group":"API Application"},{"id":"g2_accSvc","x":5500.0,"y":700.0,"width":250.0,"height":120.0,"text":"Accounts Service\n[Component: Spring Bean]","node_type":"idea","color":"#85bbf0","group":"API Application"},{"id":"g2_mfFacade","x":5200.0,"y":860.0,"width":250.0,"height":120.0,"text":"Mainframe Facade\n[Component: Spring Bean]","node_type":"idea","color":"#85bbf0","group":"API Application"},{"id":"g2_repo","x":5500.0,"y":860.0,"width":250.0,"height":120.0,"text":"Accounts Repository\n[Component: Spr